cpansec-feed (0.1.5) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fix published release directory permissions for nginx access.
  * Publish the site atomically through a current/ symlink.
  * Keep current files untouched when generated content is unchanged.
  * Add source freshness metadata to the HTML pages.
  * Include exact skip reasons in the validation report.
  * Allow the service to write published output under /var/www/cpansec-feed.
  * Publish generated assets under /var/www/cpansec-feed.
  * Make published output files world-readable for nginx.
  * Create the public output directory for the www-data group.
  * Fix /etc/default/cpansec-feed packaging path.
  * Drop tmpfiles entries that conflicted with DynamicUser.
  * Add make targets for the podman-based workflow.

